            <a href="https://66.media.tumblr.com/312a995f0b1dbc86fb8b5594a0c9b95f/tumblr_n1exca3Jp31s8s5bho1_500.gif" class="list-group-item">国内ニュース</a>
            <a href="https://67.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_m5p350PZwG1ruztjzo1_r1_500.gif" class="list-group-item">国外ニュース</a>
            <a href="https://67.media.tumblr.com/c15f3c0fe7e6d2ac3a5ae4245c93762e/tumblr_nen0rulw261rmoy1jo1_500.gif" class="list-group-item">国内サポート</a>
            <a href="https://67.media.tumblr.com/1346689c25007f38ba4e4f08378054b7/tumblr_mrgwpvXZsw1sxl7y7o1_500.gif" class="list-group-item">海外サポート</a>
            <a href="https://66.media.tumblr.com/e80c95f58608430761b7c8555bec9ce4/tumblr_mr8j6tESw41qhd8sao1_500.gif" class="list-group-item">ご連絡</a>
